metadata.name: SAI 10
metadata.description: Man sees himself as the only and only intelligent being in the universe, the owner and the only master of the world, but the reality is not like this. We are only at the beginning of the road and we still have a long way to go. The Sad Alien Invaders collection was created to remind all of us how fragile and helpless we are, and that salvation is only possible by first making peace with the world we live in and then embracing the universe.
